<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erro 500 - LearnFlow</title>
    <link href="/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full text-center">
        <div class="mb-8">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-8xl text-red-500 mb-4"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">500</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Erro Interno do Servidor
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
            Desculpe, ocorreu um erro inesperado no servidor. Nossa equipe já foi notificada e está trabalhando para resolver o problema.
        </p>
        
        <% if (error && error.message) { %>
            <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-4 mb-8 text-left">
                <p class="text-sm font-mono text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 break-all">
                    <%= error.message %>
                </p>
                <% if (error.stack) { %>
                    <details class="mt-4">
                        <summary class="text-sm text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 cursor-pointer">Ver stack trace</summary>
                        <pre class="mt-2 text-xs text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 overflow-x-auto"><%= error.stack %></pre>
                    </details>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <button onclick="window.history.back()" 
                    class="px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> Voltar
            </button>
            <a href="/inicio" 
               class="px-6 py-3 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white rounded-lg transition">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-home mr-2"></i> Ir para Início
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>